r-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eOur Honeysticks Magic 3-in-1 Little Learners Beeswax Pencils 8pk are the perfect first step into creative play. Designed as \u003cb\u003esafe, non-toxic first pencils for toddlers aged 1+\u003c\/b\u003e, these chunky, easy-grip pencils are crafted with a \u003cb\u003ebeeswax-based core, \u003c\/b\u003ehoused in\u003cb\u003e \u003c\/b\u003esustainable wood. With three creative uses in one, they invite little artists to explore drawing, painting, and even mess-free glass art.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e\u003cbr style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"\u003e\u003c!--[endif]--\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eThe purity of beeswax, now in a pencil:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eHoneysticks Pencils are the first pencils with a natural beeswax core. Made without petroleum-derived paraffin wax, they are non-toxic and safe for toddlers aged 1+ making them the perfect first pencils.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eChunky shape designed for little hands: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eEach pencil is 3.4 inches long and 0.6 inches in diameter making them easy to hold and use. Also super durable - hard to snap, crack and break by even the most energetic little hands.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eCan be used in many fun ways:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eThese pencils can be used with water for watercolour paint-like colours, or on paper, card, or even glass — giving toddlers lots of ways to play and create.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eEasy colouring with minimal pressure:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\" lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eMany coloured pencils need hard pressure to show colour, which can be tough for little hands. Honeysticks’ thick beeswax core makes colouring easy, with bright colours showing up easily.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eEasy to clean: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eSimply wipes away from smooth surfaces with a damp cloth, for no mess creative play.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eGive the gift of early creative play: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eWill make a thoughtful gift for your Little Artist, boys and girls alike. Whether as a stocking stuffer, birthday surprise, or everyday creative gift.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eSafe for play and safe for planet: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eMade with PEFC-certified wood and sustainable beeswax, Honeysticks Little Learner Pencils are a mindful choice for environmentally-conscious families.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eAt Honeysticks, we believe in a better way to play — safe, sustainable, and designed to spark imagination from the very first scribble.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look - welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550688125,"sku":"HCPLL8","price":14.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/LLP8pk_1.png?v=1765229789"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-jumbo-triangles","title":"Honeysticks Magic 3-in-1 Beeswax Pencils Jumbo Triangles 12pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW181712104 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW58227566 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW264699244 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW264699244 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW15434824 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW264699244 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eFor confident creators ready to explore bigger ideas, Honeysticks Magic 3-in-1 Jumbo Triangles 12pk are the ultimate \u003cb\u003ebeeswax colouring pencils for kids\u003c\/b\u003e. Made with a \u003cb\u003ebeeswax-based core \u003c\/b\u003eand a clever triangular design, these longer \u003cb\u003enon-toxic pencils\u003c\/b\u003e offer more control, bolder colour, and three playful ways to create.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #0f1111; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eThe purity of beeswax, now in a pencil: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #0f1111; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eHoneysticks pencils are the first pencils made with a natural beeswax core. Made without petroleum-derived paraffin wax, they are non-toxic and safe for toddlers aged 1+.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eJumbo triangle shape supports grip development: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eEach pencil is 6 inches long and 0.24 inches in diameter in an ergonomic triangular shape. Helps to support pencil grip development in older toddlers and preschoolers.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eCan be used in many fun ways: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eThese pencils can be used with water for watercolour paint-like colours, or on paper, card, or even glass — giving kids lots of ways to play and create.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eEasy colouring with minimal pressure:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003e Many coloured pencils need hard pressure to show colour, which can be tough for little hands. Honeysticks’ thick beeswax core makes colouring easy, with bright colours showing up easily.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eEasy to clean: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eSimply wipes away from smooth surfaces with a damp cloth, for no mess creative play.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eGive the gift of early creative play: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eWill make a thoughtful gift for your little artist, boys and girls alike. Whether as a stocking stuffer, birthday surprise, or everyday creative gift.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eSafe for play \u0026amp; safe for planet: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; color: #0f1111;\"\u003eMade with FSC-certified wood and sustainable beeswax, Honeysticks Jumbo Triangle Pencils are a mindful choice for environmentally-conscious families.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in safe, sustainable tools that unlock creativity at every stage.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Aptos',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Yu Gothic'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-NZ;\"\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550819197,"sku":"HCPJMT12","price":14.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/JTP12pk_1.png?v=1765230162"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-beeswax-crayons-jumbos-16pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 16pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor little artists ready to grow their drawing and writing skills, \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 16pk\u003c\/strong\u003e offer more length, control, and creative potential. These Jumbo-sized crayons are designed for little hands with a more developed pencil grip, making them perfect for finer art colouring and detailed projects.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDesigned for growing grips:\u003c\/strong\u003e At 10cm long and 1.19cm thick, Honeysticks Jumbos offer just the right balance of length and control for confident young artists aged 3+.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBright, bold colour: \u003c\/strong\u003eMade with 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade colourants – no nasties, no fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDurable and safe: \u003c\/strong\u003eTough enough to withstand serious colouring while staying safe and non-toxic.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGreat for skill building:\u003c\/strong\u003e Encourages pencil-style grip, creative control, and artistic expression.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Jumbos are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":57531702772093,"sku":"HCRJM16","price":19.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/CJ16.png?v=1765230533"},{"product_id":"honeysticks-beeswax-crayons-jumbos-24pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 24pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW184690971 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW104622780 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor little artists ready to grow their drawing and writing skills, \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Jumbos 24pk\u003c\/strong\u003e offer more length, control, and creative potential. These Jumbo-sized crayons are designed for little hands with a more developed pencil grip, making them perfect for finer art colouring and detailed projects.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDesigned for growing grips:\u003c\/strong\u003e At 10cm long and 1.19cm thick, Honeysticks Jumbos offer just the right balance of length and control for confident young artists aged 3+.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBright, bold colour: \u003c\/strong\u003eMade with 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade colourants – no nasties, no fillers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDurable and safe: \u003c\/strong\u003eTough enough to withstand serious colouring while staying safe and non-toxic.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGreat for skill building:\u003c\/strong\u003e Encourages pencil-style grip, creative control, and artistic expression.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families: \u003c\/strong\u003eDesigned by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Jumbos are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":57531740914045,"sku":"HCRJM24","price":27.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/CJ24_64124b39-fa0b-4096-a093-4ca7edf442ed.png?v=1765399837"}],"url":"https:\/\/honeysticks.co.uk\/collections\/all-products.oembed","provider":"Honeysticks UK","version":"1.0","type":"link"}